<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es" class="h-full">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>USM Events - Comunidad</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
</head>
<body class="flex flex-col min-h-full bg-gray-50 text-gray-800 font-sans">

    <nav class="bg-blue-900 text-white p-4 sticky top-0 z-50 shadow-md">
        <div class="container mx-auto flex justify-between items-center">
            <h1 class="font-bold text-xl tracking-tighter">USM <span class="text-yellow-400">EVENTS</span></h1>
            <ul class="hidden md:flex space-x-6 font-medium">
                <li><a href="index.html" class="hover:text-yellow-400 transition">Inicio</a></li>
                <li><a href="eventos.html" class="hover:text-yellow-400 transition">Eventos</a></li>
                <li><a href="comunidad.html" class="text-yellow-400 font-bold">Comunidad</a></li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <main class="flex-grow container mx-auto py-10 px-6">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-blue-900 mb-8">Espacio de la Comunidad</h2>
            
            <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-sm mb-10 border border-gray-100">
                <h3 class="font-bold mb-4 text-lg">¿Quieres organizar un evento o compartir algo?</h3>
                <form action="#" class="space-y-4">
                    <textarea class="w-full p-4 bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 rounded-xl focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 outline-none" rows="3" placeholder="Escribe aquí tu mensaje a la comunidad..."></textarea>
                    <div class="flex justify-end">
                        <button type="button" class="bg-yellow-400 text-blue-900 font-bold py-2 px-6 rounded-lg hover:bg-yellow-500 transition">Publicar</button>
                    </div>
                </form>
            </div>

            <div class="space-y-6">
                <div class="flex space-x-4 p-6 bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm">
                    <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-blue-900">SG</div>
                    <div class="flex-1">
                        <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
                            <h4 class="font-bold text-gray-900">Sebastian G. <span class="font-normal text-gray-400 text-sm ml-2">hace 2 horas</span></h4>
                        </div>
                        <p class="mt-2 text-gray-600">Se me perdieron los fonos en el J, alguien los vio? se pagan 2 lucas por el.</p>
                        <div class="mt-4 flex space-x-4 text-sm text-gray-500 font-medium">
                            <button class="hover:text-blue-600">Me gusta</button>
                            <button class="hover:text-blue-600">Responder</button>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="flex space-x-4 p-6 bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm">
                    <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-yellow-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-yellow-700">MA</div>
                    <div class="flex-1">
                        <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
                            <h4 class="font-bold text-gray-900">Maria Alarcon <span class="font-normal text-gray-400 text-sm ml-2">hace 5 horas</span></h4>
                        </div>
                        <p class="mt-2 text-gray-600">El concierto de bienvenida estuvo nashe, mande fotos a mi mama. #USMEventos</p>
                        <div class="mt-4 flex space-x-4 text-sm text-gray-500 font-medium">
                            <button class="hover:text-blue-600">Me gusta</button>
                            <button class="hover:text-blue-600">Responder</button>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>

    <footer class="bg-gray-900 text-white py-6 px-6 border-t border-gray-800">
        <div class="container mx-auto text-center">
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">Desarrollado para Taller de Lenguaje de Programación</p>
        </div>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
